OL,3,CMum dies after spending more than 40
OL,4,Chours on hospital corridor
OL,6,FA daughter has shared the lasting
OL,7,Fimpact corridor care has had on her
OL,8,Ffamily following the death of her mum,
OL,9,Fwho spent more than 40 hours on a
OL,10,Fcorridor at Glan Clwyd Hospital, near
OL,11,FRhyl.
OL,13,FChristine Simpson died aged 65, after
OL,14,Fpresenting to the accident and
OL,15,Femergency department with fluid on her
OL,16,Fchest following an X-ray. She was
OL,17,Fundergoing treatment for stomach
OL,18,Fcancer.
