OL,3,CMum dies after spending more than 40
OL,4,Chours on hospital corridor
OL,6,FHer daughter, Michelle Simpson,
OL,7,Fdescribed how her mum was left on a
OL,8,Fplastic chair for 24 hours before
OL,9,Fbeing moved to a reclining chair in
OL,10,Fthe corridor for a further 18 hours.
OL,12,FAfter being admitted to the cardiology
OL,13,Fdepartment, Michelle was told her mum
OL,14,Fwas in the wrong unit and needed to be
OL,15,Fmoved to critical care.
