OL,3,CMum dies after spending more than 40
OL,4,Chours on hospital corridor
OL,6,FMichelle recounted the moment a doctor
OL,7,Fdetailed her mum's prognosis, saying:
OL,8,F"He took me into a room a few doors
OL,9,Fdown...he said 'I am really sorry to
OL,10,Ftell you we're going to drain it
OL,11,F(Christine's chest), but it will give
OL,12,Fher months...if we don't drain it she
OL,13,Fwill have weeks'."
OL,15,FShortly after that conversation,
OL,16,FChristine died.
OL,18,FMichelle said: "Nobody told us mum was
OL,19,Fdying, they told us she had months...
OL,20,Fmum deserved a peaceful ending,
OL,21,Fsurrounded by her people.
