OL,3,CMum dies after spending more than 40
OL,4,Chours on hospital corridor
OL,6,F"I feel so guilty because I spent that
OL,7,Fwhole last day sat there, and we
OL,8,Fdidn't know she was dying... when I
OL,9,Fgot there she had nothing to eat, her
OL,10,Ffeet were swollen, she was freezing
OL,11,Fcold."
OL,13,FIt has been two years since Michelle's
OL,14,Fmum died. Michelle has since been
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with PTSD, saying: "I am
OL,16,Fjust not the same person anymore, I
OL,17,Fused to be a strong person."
