OL,6,FA Betsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,7,FBoard spokesperson said improving
OL,8,Furgent and emergency care is a top
OL,9,Fpriority and it is improving "how
OL,10,Fpeople access the right care first
OL,11,Ftime".
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, 11 November, Denbighshire
OL,14,FCounty Council passed a motion
OL,15,Frecognising the health emergency,
OL,16,Furging the health board and Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment to work together to prevent
OL,18,Funnecessary admissions.
