OL,6,FIn a statement, the chief operating
OL,7,Fofficer, Tehmeena Ajmal, at Betsi
OL,8,FCadwaladr University Health Board
OL,9,Fsaid: "Improving urgent and emergency
OL,10,Fcare is the health board's top
OL,11,Foperational priority and we are taking
OL,12,Fclear, coordinated steps to improve
OL,13,Fhow people access the right care first
OL,14,Ftime, reduce delays in emergency
OL,15,Fdepartments and for those ready to
OL,16,Fleave hospital, and ensure ambulance
OL,17,Fcrews can hand over patients safely
OL,18,Fand promptly.
