OL,6,F"We fully recognise the scale of this
OL,7,Fchallenge and are determined to
OL,8,Fdeliver lasting improvements. This
OL,9,Fwork is being driven by our Board, in
OL,10,Fpartnership with clinical and
OL,11,Foperational teams, social care
OL,12,Fcolleagues, primary care, and the
OL,13,Fthird sector.
