OL,6,F"In the longer term, our proposals to
OL,7,Fextend the range of services delivered
OL,8,Ffrom the Royal Alexandra Hospital in
OL,9,FRhyl will play a key role in
OL,10,Falleviating pressure on the emergency
OL,11,Fdepartment and hospitals wards at
OL,12,FYsbyty Glan Clwyd. The introduction of
OL,13,Fa much-needed Minor Injuries and
OL,14,FAilments Unit on the Royal Alex site
OL,15,Fwould ensure that 21,000 people from
OL,16,Fthe local area could receive care
OL,17,Fcloser to home each year.
