OL,6,F"Meanwhile, up to 220 people each year
OL,7,Fwho currently receive inpatient care
OL,8,Fat Ysbyty Glan Clwyd or a neighbouring
OL,9,Fcommunity hospital would benefit from
OL,10,Four proposals to establish an
OL,11,Fintegrated Community Reablement
OL,12,FFacility at the Royal Alex. This would
OL,13,Fsee health and social care staff
OL,14,Fworking together as part of an
OL,15,Fintegrated model of care which draws
OL,16,Fon examples of best practice from
OL,17,Facross the United Kingdom."
